## Introduction

This is simple todo app, build rust and actix-web. This isn't best practice, but easly to understand for begginer to start for creating rest api using rust programming language and actix-web as framework.

## Prerequiste

- Rust

## Installation

#### Setup Rust

Follow installation instruction from official website - [Click Here](rust-lang.org/tools/install)

#### Install Diesel CLI

```bash
cargo install diesel_cli
```

#### Clone Repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/nukumalik/actix-web-todo-rest-api.git
cd actix-web-todo-rest-api
```

Rename `.env.example` file

```bash
mv .env.example .env
```

Run program

```bash
cargo run
```

### Depdencies

- actix-web
- diesel
- dotenv
- serde
- serde_json
